snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play Beauty Salon
snippet.description:
Diana plays beauty salon with dolls. Little girl use hair toys and makeup toys for kids. But the girl wants to play for real and calls in the game of the brother. Diana makes Roma a face mask. And when Diana took the make-up toys, Roma runs away. Fun pretend play video for kids. 
Diana`s INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
